    p Content could then be divided into very few mandatory story beats with authored dialogue or even cutscenes; and recommended or optional content with bits of explicit story elements at their beginning / end (the only choke points we can ensure will exist, though we may find more oportunities to trigger more), along with supplementary, stimuli-triggered, abstracted AI dialogue.

